@Node Description "Description"

  Description
  ===========

    The account editor is what a co/sysop uses to edit user accounts
    and grant users access to the system.

@EndNode

@Node Installation "Installation"

  Installation
  ============

    This is installed as part of HydraBBS's default set-up.

    It is stored as HBBS:Doors/User/AccountEdit/AccountEdit.HBBS

    The following lines have been added to HBBS:Commands/System

    AccountEdit_Type_1=HBBS
    AccountEdit_Door_1=HBBS:Doors/User/AccountEdit/AccountEdit.HBBS {N} {O}

    The following lines have been added to HBBS:Commands/Level_255

    Accounts_Type_1=HBBS
    Accounts_Door_1=HBBS:Doors/User/AccountEdit/AccountEdit.HBBS {N} {O}

@EndNode

